title: ...can anyone peg this odd font? / wide techno style w/ rounded edges, square counters
content:
...Me and my sales rep have been tryin to figure this one out for DAYS now. Found a few that were close, but not dead on. any thoughts would be greatly appreciated.

comments.content: Based on the poorly drawn curves and the inexplicable t, I'd wager that this is either custom or a free font.
